<ab facs="#facs_376_r2l25"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> icht <expan>gearbeıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd
                        darcʒu gedienen / ob es cʒu gute </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_376_r2l26">vnd frıden kumen möchte das
                            <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tun
